{"tid":1292515,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港演員魏惠文拎綜援演大茄孤獨一世","createTime":"2019-07-07T11:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T14:44:51.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8f15003c0e7e0f4116c59a5c31122c6da597855","tid":1292515,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MIH-jcMzqrY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMIH-jcMzqrY&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakTpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=42646a2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MIH-jcMzqrY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001.html&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakTpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=6df7e7aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n「人生有幾多個十年」，有些演員不用等就已經片約不斷，但有些演員等足兩個十年，才有人生中的第一個機會，魏惠文就是後者。他，1990年在演藝學院畢業，1996年加入TVB，2016年在《城寨英雄》飾演林穎彤衰老竇「爛賭發」，因而開始為人熟悉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=6dc579ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n魏惠文接受《娛場》主持人李文珊訪問時，淡淡說出他的過去。因為喜歡演戲，所以他報讀了演藝學院戲劇系，同屆同學有李婉華、陳錦鴻、劉玉翠、關寶慧等等，不過他畢業後前景並不明朗：「一年到晚都只係去Casting，你想求、想做都冇人請，我真係試過畢業之後，頭三個月只係搵到二千幾蚊。」"},{"pid":"8c311b233a6b0099bdb48d67f95114b6480cd52e","tid":1292515,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:04:52.000Z","msg":"1996年，魏惠文加入TVB，演過無數過行行企企的閒角。而問到稍為有戲份的角色，魏惠文就苦笑說有《緣來沒法擋》的地產舖老闆、《秀才遇着兵》的變態殺人犯以及《怒火街頭》滕麗名的衰老公。演活過無數個小人物，街坊對魏惠文的印象大約就是記得他是電視從業員，但從來不知道他叫甚麼名字。而最難堪的一次，就是他搭巴士，被一位小妹妹稱呼作演員最忌諱的三個字：「個妹妹落車去到樓梯時，就同爸爸大聲講：『爸爸，我見到TVB個茄喱啡呀！』即使你幾努力、幾用功，都唔代表你會有成績。被人講到係一位演員，已經唔係一件容易嘅事，你諗下你做咗茄喱啡廿幾年。」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_04b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=6902d767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">現實生活中，佢事業、家庭、愛情都唔順利。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n遇上低潮，有人會谷底反彈，可是有人卻低處未算低。2010年，魏惠文接拍了《巾幗梟雄之義海豪情》，當時要求他做一位日本漢奸，需說六句日文對白。可是拍了四小時，他卻完全失準，一句對白都講不到，其後更晦氣地說：「其實觀眾都未必識聽日文啦‥‥‥」這句說話很快就傳到監製李添勝的耳邊，令他大為震怒。為了平息對方怒火，魏惠文希望可以約見李添勝解釋此事，可惜對方不願接見‥‥‥"},{"pid":"9d737c40d029b393ccd4f5ecba209142be4b231a","tid":1292515,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:06:36.000Z","msg":"隨着演出機會愈來愈少，魏惠文更珍惜每個演出時刻。在TVB等足廿年，他在2016年終於遇到《城寨英雄》「爛賭發」的角色，縱使這個角色是多麼的不討好，又即使此角色是「執三攤」，魏惠文都絕不介意，用心演好，終於他得到外界認同了。不過這一次取得成功，原來都是關乎他的悲慘經歷。他苦笑說：「我家姐、阿哥喺幾年之間都發生車禍，撞到入ICU。家姐就斷手斷腳，哥哥車禍後患上思覺失調。跟住我媽媽中風引致腦退化，我冇得揀，要申請綜援。」有些人遇到困難，總有另一半替自己分憂，可是魏惠文至今仍然形單影隻，單身足足超過三十年，他說：「一生嘅Timing唔啱，基本上我覺得我冇可能有另一半，可以話係擁抱單身嘅階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n<br />\n事業、愛情、家庭都不順暢，魏惠文沒有選擇放棄，反而繼續默默堅守：「希望可以等到下一個《城寨英雄》嘅機會啦！」"},{"pid":"22f5538f608b83bfd6bb449e7d4780bed91f7c4d","tid":1292515,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_02b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=d93f8537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">魏惠文喺TVB演活過好多小人物角色。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_03b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=581ae010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">浮浮沉沉多年，試過當街被小妹妹嗌做茄喱啡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_04b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=6902d767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">現實生活中，佢事業、家庭、愛情都唔順利。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_05b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=e827b240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">第一套稍有戲份嘅角色，係《緣來沒法擋》飾演地產舖老闆。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_06b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=b0391b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">喺《怒火街頭》，魏惠文飾演滕麗名嘅衰老公。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_07b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=311c7e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">喺《秀才遇着兵》，佢飾演變態殺人狂。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_08b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=d2097586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">可惜，佢喺《巾幗梟雄之義海豪情》中表現失準而得罪監製李添勝。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_09b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=532c10a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2016年，魏惠文憑《城寨英雄》「爛賭發」一角而為人熟悉。</span></div>"},{"pid":"c8132630a64b063a916cb9d1a64fc700484f91ec","tid":1292515,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:12:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_10b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_10b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=a58fd936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">讀書時代嘅魏惠文</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_11b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_11b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=24aabc11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">當時佢拎住獎杯都幾威威</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_12b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_12b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=7cb41539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中學畢業後，佢讀演藝學院，同期同學有李婉華、梁榮忠、劉玉翠等。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_13b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_13b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=fd91701e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">魏惠文與King Sir合照</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_14b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_14b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=cc894769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔經唔覺，魏惠文喺TVB已經廿幾年啦。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190704/photo/bkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_15b.jpg?20190705154636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190704110046368-0704_00862_001_15b.jpg%3F20190705154636&h=4dac224e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">去年，魏惠文有份參演舞台劇《奪命證人》，並與劉嘉玲合照。</span></div>"},{"pid":"565f77b17c69e9bd7b73b70a9513a5f2e703af26","tid":1292515,"uid":182127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab33d1bb3b0c4abd061442fecf3c800cefb5523","tid":1292515,"uid":258513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:14:25.000Z","msg":"人生如戲 戲如人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503411b501eacc97acac0fe3c99a8519d0fca0e0","tid":1292515,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:21:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">網民回應</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/07/uJGUeS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F07%2FuJGUeS.png&h=516fda1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/07/aQ8hsZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F07%2FaQ8hsZ.png&h=6819d0cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9072dd086ede2a571ace39352641cddc380caf38","tid":1292515,"uid":242444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:44:51.000Z","msg":"我諗tvb大部分嗌唔出名既演員都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}